{"tid":731341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"敘利亞武裝組織公開被綁架3年的日本記者影像","createTime":"2018-07-06T06:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T11:55:17.000Z","uid":22590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ddbd3c06e32aa9fcae32f2fe209af9f6eff28d","tid":731341,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ctee.com.tw/livenews/gj/20180706001126-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ctee.com.tw%2Flivenews%2Fgj%2F20180706001126-260408&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=eee24de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ctee.com.tw/livenews/gj/20180706001126-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n安田在影片中說:「我是純平。我很好，祝願家人平安無事。只是我很想見家人，希望能馬上見到。」他還說:「請不要把我忘記」、「希望別放棄」。 日本電視台拿到的影片的拍攝日期是「2017年10月17日」。<br />\n<br />\n安田是在2015年6月下旬進入敘利亞，綁架他的是從國際恐怖組織蓋達脫離的「敘利亞解放組織」。報導指出，本週在敘利亞和該組織接觸的人物表示，「安田現在的健康狀況非常糟」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，武裝組織方面是想藉由公開影像，催促日本政府與之談判，商談釋放安田的條件。<br />\n<br />\n乜呢條友仲在生 家陣肥肥白白<br />\n去扮人質分錢?<br />\n3年永住叙利亞未?"},{"pid":"24e86fcbcf60e59c6797156e935ebac071771478","tid":731341,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20160530/photo/bknint-20160530134910124-0530_17011_001_01p.jpg?20160530181000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160530%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20160530134910124-0530_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20160530181000&h=8fc489fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"136080fc399e0221d2b054f4bd84e4a1993004fd","tid":731341,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"即係養左佢三年??"}]}